{
  "stem": "12402.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was a nurse under false identification, you know, like-- She survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I met the girl there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she told me-- I told about her brother-- I met him in Munich.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- so on-- so we were standing-- we were there in Stuttgart, and I couldn't do no business.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I contact my family, I forgot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "While in Stuttgart, we contact-- no before that, we contact our family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know how I got-- I remembered an address.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And finally they found that we're alive, and they tried to make papers for us to get us into Canada.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they warned me, don't smuggle, don't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Once you get caught, black market, so you could never come into Canada or anywhere.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we-- we suffered with it, and you had to eat what they gave us, you know, like provision.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had kitchens, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we-- so we-- I'm getting to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So from Stuttgart-- so my kid brother worked in a camp, so he had all kind of bread he used to bring me, not far from was another camp, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- the military-- we got the papers for my brothers, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it took us maybe a year-- they had no passage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had no transportation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no planes in those years, and no boats, but the one ship was going from Bremerhaven, from Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we waited for the-- for that ship to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it left, I think, the ship left in-- in July, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we got out of the ship, and we traveled maybe till end of August, August the 27th.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We arrived in Canada at the port of Halifax.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
